@Override public synchronized void checkExit(final int status) {     this.status = status.     ++count.     throw new SecurityException("SystemExitTrackingSecurityManager is installed. JVM will not exit"). }
public synchronized int getStatus() {     checkState(isSystemExitCalled()).     return status. }
public synchronized boolean isSystemExitCalled() {     return getCount() > 0. }
public synchronized int getCount() {     return count. }
